				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">IMHO, in a group, mages primary responsibilities are to:
<br />

<br />
* Supply constant, high DPS
<br />

<br />
* When situations warrant, DS the party (Debuffers/slowers/clerics get hit too...)
<br />

<br />
* Assist with mana to other players (rods)
<br />

<br />
* Most importantly, maintain a significant mana pool to be able to burn down multiple mobs when things go wrong
<br />

<br />
and don't forget
<br />

<br />
* Provide hours of entertainment with occasional use of Envenomed Sleeves<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=568700" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
