umm no if ya go oom / lom,  ya playing ya class to it fullest, On addys I can go very very low on mana, even on normal addys, maybe its that we tend to do a addy in 15-20min, no slower or cler, or sometimes we go in with 4 of a class, me, bst, monk and a cler. most times i do them with speed in my mind I like down time to be able to do other things in RL <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" />.
