				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Itchyban said it well.  One thing I would add is that we malo/malosinia, unless the shammy does it.
<br />

<br />
Typical group situation for me:
<br />

<br />
1.  Make rods, pet gear, and focus stuff for peeps as they join the group
<br />
2.  Get to camp, make pet (usually water in a grp), outfit it, burnout and shrink it
<br />
3.  Group DS on pull
<br />
4.  Malasinia on pull, send pet once tank has agro
<br />
5.  Rain at around 75%, nuke at 60ish. Whatever works, just not too early
<br />
6.  Lose roll on loot
<br />
7.  Repeat<br />_________________<br />Ragi 65 Mage of 7th Hammer</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
