Almost true...the debuff you get at your level (or any level) will generate <span style="font-style: italic">some</span> aggro, but not enough to prevent a warrior from whacking the mob a few times to regain it.  Usually I find that I can outaggro an arrow and that is about it, <span style="text-decoration: underline">unless</span> I get a resist then it is a whole different ballgame.
